Day 91: Ansible Lineinfile Module

Date: December 17, 2025
Overview
Modified specific lines in configuration files.
Key Concepts Learned

Lineinfile module
Regular expressions
Line insertion/replacement
Backup options

Playbook
yaml- name: Configure SSH settings
  lineinfile:
    path: /etc/ssh/sshd_config
    regexp: '^PermitRootLogin'
    line: 'PermitRootLogin no'
    backup: yes

Challenges Faced
Writing correct regex patterns and avoiding unintended line modifications.
